---
title: Chermoula Pork & Carrot Couscous for Dinner with Pork & Pumpkin Salad with Yoghurt Dressing for Lunch
description: Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for tomorrow’s lunch. Start
off dinner with a chermoula spiced pork on a bed of fluffy couscous that can be transformed into a refreshing salad with roasted pumpkin.

